branch strategy --

main -- deployed branch
staging -- testing
feature branch -- top level branch for new work implementations awaiting official staging test runs

todos -- standalone branch, (wont merge to staging) managing project roadmap organized within the todo's folder - broken down to hierarchical readme's (mechanics, level design, character design, etc)
